_header: Deem as you list I am content
Note: For a less defiant version in one couplet, see 1110.
_description: Warning to his mistress, by W. Coullicke — one quatrain

CamFitzMc182.Transcription:
Deme as you list I am contentSo as you deme not wrongfullyA
                    wrongfull dome thou must repentYf prudent iudges do it trye
CamFitzMc182.Note:
Added by a hand of sixteenth century, written twice on f.
                        138v, again once on f. 139.
